Hence, &amp;ldquo;RTWZ&amp;rdquo; is the odd one.<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/20/08/Common_Diagram_28.01.2020_D1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 536px; height: 128px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

